Avoid using 'water' and be careful not to combine *all* ingredients in your inventory, as this might reset your score.

message: Focus on proteins and grains. Always use the 'stove' on raw proteins (egg, beef, bacon) to cook them and increase their value to 20. Then, combine two cooked proteins to get an item worth 40. Finally, add a grain (bread, tortilla, wheat, corn) or sometimes a vegetable (potato, broccoli) to this two-protein item to reach a high score of 60. Three distinct ingredients (two proteins + one grain/veg) seems to be the sweet spot. Don't use the 'water' tool; it does nothing. Don't combine all items in your inventory, as this can drop your score to zero.
